name: Simple Bidirectional Visitor Counter using Arduino Uno
body:
### Welcome
This is the website hosted by GitHub Pages for the project designed by Advait Ambeskar (@advaitambeskar) using Arduino Uno in the third year of his course in Electronics Engineering.

### Authors and Contributors
This project was implemented by Advait Ambeskar (@advaitambeskar), Sayli Dalvi and Hetal Gosavi. Any error is regretted.
